'''鰤屬'''（{{lang|la|'''''Seriola'''''}}），又譯'''塞里奥拉属'''<ref name=bowenwang>{{cite web |url=http://science.bowenwang.com.cn/animals-amberjack.htm |title=琥珀鱼 |accessdate=2013-04-30 |language=zh-hans |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121052617/http://science.bowenwang.com.cn/animals-amberjack.htm |archivedate=2011-11-21 }}</ref>，是[[有骨魚|有骨魚]]的一個屬，俗稱作「琥珀魚」<ref name=bowenwang /><ref>{{cite episode |date=2013-04-30 |url=http://mytv.tvb.com/foodandtravel/japanflavour/144433 |episode=《[[J_Food好吃|J Food好吃]]》 |channel=[[J2|J2]] |language=zh-sg }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。現存的物種有九種，儘管過往這九個物種被分為更多的物種<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fishbase.org/NomenClature/ScientificNameSearchList.php?crit1_fieldname=SYNONYMS.SynGenus&crit1_fieldtype=CHAR&crit1_operator=EQUAL&crit1_value=Seriola&crit2_fieldname=SYNONYMS.SynSpecies&crit2_fieldtype=CHAR&crit2_operator=contains&crit2_value=&group=summary&backstep=-2&sortby=validname |title=FishBase: ''Seriola'' |access-date=2013-05-03 |archive-date=2015-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118154656/http://www.fishbase.org/NomenClature/ScientificNameSearchList.php?crit1_fieldname=SYNONYMS.SynGenus&crit1_fieldtype=CHAR&crit1_operator=EQUAL&crit1_value=Seriola&crit2_fieldname=SYNONYMS.SynSpecies&crit2_fieldtype=CHAR&crit2_operator=contains&crit2_value=&group=summary&backstep=-2&sortby=validname |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而又有一些過往被劃歸鰤屬的物種，現時已被劃歸[[鰺科|鰺科]]的其他屬。

==物種==
本屬現時包括以下九個物種<ref>{{FishBase genus | genus = Seriola| month = February | year = 2013}}</ref>：
*[[卡彭氏鰤|卡彭氏鰤]] ''Seriola carpenteri'' <small>[[Frank_Jewett_Mather_III|F. J. Mather]], 1971</small> (Guinean amberjack)
* [[高體鰤|高體鰤]] ''Seriola dumerili'' ：又稱紅甘鰺、杜氏鰤。<small>([[Antoine_Risso|A. Risso]], 1810)</small> (Greater amberjack)
*[[斑紋鰤|斑紋鰤]] ''Seriola fasciata'' <small>([[Marcus_Elieser_Bloch|Bloch]], 1793)</small> (Lesser amberjack)
*[[馬鰤|馬鰤]] ''Seriola hippos'' <small>[[Albert_Günther|Günther]], 1876</small> (Samson fish)
* [[黄条鰤|黄条鰤]] ''Seriola lalandi'' <small>[[Achille_Valenciennes|Valenciennes]], 1833</small> (Yellowtail amberjack)
*[[祕魯鰤|祕魯鰤]] ''Seriola peruana''<small>[[Franz_Steindachner|Steindachner]], 1881</small> (Fortune jack)
* [[鰤魚|五條鰤]] ''Seriola quinqueradiata'' ：又稱黃尾鰺。<small>[[Coenraad_Jacob_Temminck|Temminck]] & [[Hermann_Schlegel|Schlegel]], 1845</small> (Japanese amberjack)
* [[長鰭鰤|長鰭鰤]] ''Seriola rivoliana'' <small>[[Achille_Valenciennes|Valenciennes]], 1833</small> (Almaco jack, highfin jack)
*[[環帶鰤|環帶鰤]] ''Seriola zonata'' <small>([[Samuel_Latham_Mitchill|Mitchill]], 1815)</small> (Banded rudderfish)

